Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, I'll sprinkle on some herbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I brought it over freshly baked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is done, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that smells good!\NI'm sure I'll feel great after eating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skin will be smoother, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you getting used to living in Clarines?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I thought I'd start\Nlooking for a job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who don't work don't eat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:01:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the capital of the\Nkingdom of Clarines, Wistal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my unusual red hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the prince of Tanbarun wanted\Nto force me to be his concubine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so I left the country\Nwhere I was born and raised
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to start a new life by myself\Nin this neighboring kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to go along with the flow of fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but Zen, the second prince\Nof Clarines, lent me his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the country I've settled in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The town I've settled in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The road I've settled on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:13.69,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 2: Following the Sound of Your Heart"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gardener... painter...\Ncarriage repair factory worker...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Herbalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd like to work as an herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we don't need anyone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However... you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't judge based on looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do if your\Nregular customer heard you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They have so many rare medicinal herbs\Nthat I can't get a hold of back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but they also have\Ntypes that I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he your regular customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's still young, but he's\Na respectable court herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Court...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you already know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but only the most knowledgeable and\Nskillful herbalists can become court herbalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarines is a country with deep pockets\Nthat will support any talented persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing. Clarines is very\Nadvanced in the study of medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's information on\Nbecoming a court herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you pass the test that's held once a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be able to work in\NWistal Castle as an apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're an herbalist,\Nwhy don't you try taking the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is pretty difficult, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm here to see Kiki\Nor Mitsuhide from the royal guards...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Could you be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies. We have been informed\Nthat you are a guest of Prince Zen's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Prince Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... What are you doing, Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just getting a little exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't have my body getting soft\Nwith all that deskwork I've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you snuck out when\Nyou were supposed to be doing deskwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't seen your face in a while, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could finally see you, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've come here\Nfor a reason, right, Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. You told me to tell you\Nwhen I was going outside of town, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--All right, let's go! Right now!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys, make something\Nup to tell Mitsuhide for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen! Where are--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mount Koto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain beyond the sea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to a place like that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that a lot of\Nmedicinal herbs grow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stock up and\Nstudy more about medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so the town pharmacist told\Nme of a few promising places.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, study? But aren't you already an herbalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but there's still a lot I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to learn more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll bring you to\Nthe forest here tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarines is a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Mom, why's it so red?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That lady's hair is bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Stop it. Eat your food quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks delicious, like an apple, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Mom, I want to eat an\Napple now! Let's go eat one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Apple, apple...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because people from different\Ncountries come and go here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All the different cultures are mixed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Prince Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got some good wine. How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today. I'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a wine seller I met before in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've bought souvenirs for\Nmy soldiers from him ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, why do you keep escaping from the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Raj of Tanbarun\Nalways orders his servants
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring the things he wants to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he gets upset when\Nthey don't bring him what he wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone's sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You said earlier, didn't you?\NThat this country was charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like there are still mountains\Nof charm that I haven't discovered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to see more, to learn more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good herbs are needed for good medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good land is needed for good herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn more about this land\Nand the herbs that grow here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're kind of similar, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I need to get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you find some good herbs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'll be back before dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that red hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's unusual...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'd get a good price for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make some good medicines with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the escape today was worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you can do the rest of the\Ndeskwork in high spirits, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki's working hard, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shirayuki Effect is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me greeting you\Nat the bottom of the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it such an innocent thing as a greeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have business with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, I wouldn't be talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about something\Na prince couldn't even get his hands on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who it's presented to, it should\Nbring in a huge reward, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, a red-haired girl born\Ndecorated with natural jewels... or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you're going to sell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How vulgar! I said, "presented."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There are tons of rich\Npeople with strange tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you even think of something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I could also wait until it grew out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be too bad to\Nkeep you by my side until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Red?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Shirayuki's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I brought bread to her room\Nthis morning, but she wasn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no light in\Nher room last night, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what in the world happened to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's some food. You wanna eat, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You little--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she saw away at the rope all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the keys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no way out, was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he on the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, you're in\Nthe middle of a mountain, Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you could get out, do you\Nthink you could escape by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have a place I decided to go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you should try someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you decide to stop running, Red?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you won't complain if I catch you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I burned herbs with paralyzing effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so the feeling in your body\Nshould be numbed for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rest well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:16:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was on the second floor earlier\Nbecause he didn't want me going up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's a way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no bars!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, this is it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Those herbs earlier didn't really\Nhave that much of an effect, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape from me on this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? If you run away now,\Nsomeone else'll probably just come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be safer if you just gave\Nyourself to some noble or royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be protected and live in luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that'd be a good way to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you, Red?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in that path!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll bring you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there, bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't this supposed to be a day trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a guard, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? I was planning to take\Nthat job for myself wherever I presented her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and make some money while I was at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought about that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. This mansion used to be my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Our vacation home from\Nwhen we were still nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you knew it so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I can only live in hiding like a stray dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, this was a\Npretty gorgeous house, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Social status and family name can be\Nswallowed up by darkness in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,People like you who wear\Nnice clothes and act all elegant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,will have nothing left if you lose your fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait until you're covered with filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't live like this any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how, but I'm gonna\Nmake money no matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:19:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I thought I could use you, Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any desire to know\Nhow this girl looks in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki is not here to\Nbe used as anyone's tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name's Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't soil her name!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? Are you her dad or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dad...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, was there anyone with this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's by himself, we can just\Ntake him down the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't escort\Nhim all the way to the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we can just hand him over to an\Nofficial at the bottom of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Castle? Who in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, as in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...the second prince of Clarines?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shirayuki's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use this on that man's injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Red. Where is the place you\Nsaid you wanted to go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Start walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,From what the officials said, that Mihaya\Ndidn't seem to be connected to any bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But just in case, I'll be more\Ncareful of my surroundings for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, are you angr--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, will you look\Nthis way for just a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, you came to find me...\Nwords aren't enough, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank y--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Five seconds was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,More than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I was a little angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to explain,\Nbut it was more at myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun just learning more\Nabout things outside the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But after learning about them,\NI wonder about what I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, what that mountain monkey asked\Nyou when he left that you didn't answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The place you decided to go by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the reason I decided\Nto come to this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see how you live in this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the place where I'll be able to\Ndo that is where I've decided to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:22:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can see you from that place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, I want to say thanks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for being unhurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.53,0:22:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the country I've settled in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The town I've settled in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The road I've settled on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I end up at a standstill,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's the place I chose for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure a dazzling wind will blow at my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.77,0:24:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, your country is great, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl has expectations\Nand will take advantage of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to go for it, so I came to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So that red-haired girl\Nis Prince Zen's friend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.53,0:24:20.08,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 3: Shining Time of Promise"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a vulgar color...
